properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 5 at 7:33AM EST until February 7 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...South to Southwest winds 15 to 25 kt becoming West on
Friday with occasional gusts up to 35 kt and seas 4 to 6 feet
expected.

* WHERE...Flagler Beach to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...From 10 AM Thursday to 10 AM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THURSDAY TO 10 AM EST FRIDAY
